<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddc8d094c-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee" identifier="/us/usc/t2/s173"><num value="173">§ 173.</num><heading> Establishment of Center for the Book</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There is hereby established in the Library of Congress a Center for the Book.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Center shall be under the direction of the Librarian of Congress.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddc8d094d-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/129/s3">Pub. L. 95–129, § 3</ref>, <date date="1977-10-13">Oct. 13, 1977</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/91/1151">91 Stat. 1151</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
